Want to learn about some AWS services while you're waiting for your next virtual re:Invent session to start? Are you an AWS expert and want to test your knowledge? That's why we built the Stackery re:Invent Quiz game! Well, that and your chance to get some AWS credits and an Echo if you deploy this skill to your AWS account with Stackery. Learn more at stackery.io/blog/reinvent-alexa-quiz-challenge!
